# Summary
This documentation explains how Amplitude identifies unique users through a system of Device ID, User ID, and Amplitude ID, detailing how these IDs interact across different scenarios including anonymous browsing, multi-device usage, and user login states, as well as how Amplitude handles user merging when it determines multiple Amplitude IDs belong to the same user.

